    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shoes, sandals or slippers which body or a significant part of the footwear is elaborately decorated with beads. The beads, which are not always but typically sewn on, usually decorate the footwear with patterns or motifs such as geometric patterns, floral and animal motifs.</Note_Text>
